title: Big Brother's Cat and Lawson strip down for naked tour | Daily Mail Online
text: They entertained viewers with their antics on the 2015 season of Big Brother. And it looks like Lawson and Cat are still bringing the entertainment, this time as naked magicians. The pair took to Instagram on Monday night to post a VERY racy photo of themselves, and two co-workers, posing completely nude as part of their The Naked Magicians U.S. tour. Where to look? Big Brother's Lawson Reeves and Cat Law stripped down as part of their Naked Magicians tour this week The three men in the photo, including Lawson, covered their manhood with strategically placed top hats. Meanwhile, Cat covered herself by holding a stuffed bunny rabbit over her nether-regions whilst cupping her breasts with her arm. '@cwmagic and @miketylermagic congratulations on the success so far of your second @thenakedmagicians US tour,' Lawson captioned the image. 'Hopefully no one has been able to top this meet and greet photo,' Lawson captioned the photo Flashback: Cat and Lawson found love on season 11 of Big Brother, which saw Lawson cheat on his girlfriend of 5 years to be with the blonde beauty 'Hopefully no one has been able to top this meet and greet photo.' Fans were quick to comment on the image, with one writing: 'E .' Another said: 'Woah, good for you guys! Rocking your confidence.' True love: Almost three years after meeting, the couple are still going strong Cat and Lawson found love on season 11 of Big Brother, which saw Lawson cheat on his girlfriend of 5 years to be with the blonde beauty. Now, almost three years later, the couple are still going strong. Lawson currently works as a magician, while Cat acts as his glamorous on stage assistant.
